  "pageTitle": "C&D 廢棄物利用線",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page case-study-detail-page case-study-detail-page-industrial\">\n      <section class=\"section page-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"case-detail-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">C&amp;D 廢棄物箱 詳情</p>\n        <h1 id=\"case-detail-title\">C&D 廢棄物利用線</h1>\n        <p class=\"hero-copy\">綜合C&D 廢棄物回收管線的參考資料，生產回收骨料及分離可回收材料。</p>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section case-detail-section case-detail-timeline-section\" id=\"construction-waste-utilization\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-waste-utilization-timeline-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">參考時間軸</p>\n          <h2 id=\"construction-waste-utilization-timeline-title\">從掩埋場壓力到可回收的輸出流</h2>\n          <p>案例依買方評估流程排序：背景、合作單位、限制、解決方案，以及前後比較。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"case-detail-timeline\" aria-label=\"案例 詳情 時間軸\">\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>01</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">專案背景</p>\n              <h3>建築與裝飾廢棄物所需利用價值</h3>\n              <p>該專案將混合的建築與裝飾廢棄物處理成可重複使用的輸出流，而非直接將材料導向掩埋壓力。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>物料類別</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">2 串流</strong><span>建築與裝飾浪費</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>輸出方向</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">3 輸出</strong><span>骨料/金屬/輕質材料</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>02</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">合作單位</p>\n              <h3>匿名區域C&D 廢棄物利用公司</h3>\n              <p>合作單位正在擴展骨料回收，需要一條可參考的生產線，讓買家能依廢棄物類型、場址狀況及設備範圍進行比較。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>操作員類型</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 區域團隊</strong><span>廢棄物利用公司</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>評論焦點</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">4 檢查</strong><span>資料/場地/範圍/影片</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>03</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">實際限制</p>\n              <h3>戶外車場的後勤安排塑造了鐵路線的配置</h3>\n              <p>佈局必須考慮裝載機供料、設備基礎區域、骨料堆積、金屬收集及輕型物料分離處理。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>場地區域</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">5 區域</strong><span>給料至庫存</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>初選限制</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 場地</strong><span>戶外物流足跡</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>04</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">解法</p>\n              <h3>70 t/h Lion One 線路整合分離</h3>\n              <p>該設備範圍結合了給料、破碎、篩選、磁性分離、氣流分離、輸送、粉塵控制介面及輸出收集。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>容量參考</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">70 t/h</strong><span>Lion One線</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>核心流程</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">4 製程</strong><span>壓碎 / 顯示屏 / 磁鐵 / 氣流</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>05</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">前後對比</p>\n              <h3>參考套件顯示了更清晰的回收路徑</h3>\n              <div class=\"case-detail-comparison\">\n                <div><span>之前</span><strong>混合場地材料且路由清晰度低</strong><p>建築與裝飾廢棄物需經過多次處理步驟，才能看到可回收的部分。</p></div>\n                <div><span>之後</span><strong>從給料到儲存的整合流程</strong><p>影像佔地面積涵蓋給料、破碎、篩分、磁性分離、氣流分離及最終輸出堆。</p></div>\n              </div>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>影像範圍</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">6 步驟</strong><span>餵料到輸出</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section case-detail-action-section industrial-rfq-section ai-layout-reference\" aria-label=\"案例操作\">\n        <div class=\"rfq-action-strip case-detail-action-strip\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">請求參考包</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/case-studies\">返回案例研究</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
